CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1941, pg. 12 reads: "National Officers, Delegates And Visitors To Debs About Town Confab In Pittsburgh"...bottom, left to right; Betty... Mae Bailey, Louise...and Ellen Kraft Dammons.- Harris Photos"
TitMainTitle: Debs About Town members, front left Betty, Louise, and Ellen Kraft Dammons, posed on Loendi Club porch
